%% Model Registry - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Dashboard
    participant Istio as Istio Gateway<br/>mTLS STRICT
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>Proxy Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ISCtrl as InferenceService<br/>Controller
    participant KServePod as KServe Pod<br/>(init container)
    participant CSI as CSI Storage<br/>Initializer
    participant S3 as Model Artifact<br/>Storage (S3)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant BFF as UI BFF<br/>8080/TCP
    participant Catalog as Model Catalog<br/>8080/TCP
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    Client->>Istio: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Istio->>MR: Forward (mTLS)<br/>Service Identity
    MR->>DB: INSERT model metadata<br/>Auth: Username/Password<br/>Encryption: TLS 1.2+ (configurable)
    DB-->>MR: Success
    MR-->>Istio: 201 Created (JSON)
    Istio-->>Client: Response

    Note over K8sAPI,MR: Flow 2: InferenceService Sync via Controller
    K8sAPI->>ISCtrl: Watch Event: InferenceService<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    ISCtrl->>MR: POST/PUT inference_services<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    MR-->>ISCtrl: 200 OK
    ISCtrl->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService status/finalizers<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over KServePod,S3: Flow 3: Model Download via CSI Storage Initializer
    KServePod->>CSI: Resolve model-registry:// URI
    CSI->>MR: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/model_artifacts<br/>8080/TCP HTTP plaintext
    MR-->>CSI: Artifact location (S3 URI)
    CSI->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Storage credentials
    S3-->>CSI: Model artifacts
    CSI-->>KServePod: Model files ready

    Note over Browser,DB: Flow 4: UI Frontend to BFF to Model Registry
    Browser->>BFF: GET /api/v1/model_registry/:id/registered_models<br/>Auth: User Token<br/>TLS 1.3 (optional)
    BFF->>MR: Proxy to Model Registry API<br/>Auth: Internal SA Token<br/>Istio mTLS (if in-mesh)
    MR->>DB: SELECT metadata<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>MR: Results
    MR-->>BFF: JSON Response
    BFF->>K8sAPI: Verify user permissions<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    K8sAPI-->>BFF: Auth result
    BFF-->>Browser: Filtered JSON Response

    Note over Catalog,HF: Flow 5: Catalog Source Loading
    Browser->>BFF: GET /api/v1/model_catalog/models<br/>Auth: User Token
    BFF->>Catalog: GET /api/model_catalog/v1alpha1/models<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Catalog->>HF: GET model metadata<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    HF-->>Catalog: Model catalog data
    Catalog-->>BFF: Catalog results
    BFF-->>Browser: Formatted catalog response
